elements.2211.03148_110456afe789a78e04aa8e250a7b9: Deep Ensemble Convolutional Neural Networks has become a methodology of choice for analyzing medical images with a diagnostic performance comparable to a physician, including the diagnosis of Diabetic Retinopathy
elements.2211.03148_80c6a69605e7ac2be7b9e2ef36cef: However, commonly used techniques are deterministic and are therefore unable to provide any estimate of predictive uncertainty
elements.2211.03148_933bb688a7db9081e5e3c5813f280: Quantifying model uncertainty is crucial for reducing the risk of misdiagnosis
elements.2211.03148_547eedb0451d26fffd255c9ab6501: A reliable architecture should be well-calibrated to avoid over-confident predictions
elements.2211.03148_13181e22d90b2b7d6b9e0c3ed4b26: To address this, we propose a UATTA-ENS: Uncertainty-Aware Test-Time Augmented Ensemble Technique for 5 Class PIRC Diabetic Retinopathy Classification to produce reliable and well-calibrated predictions
elements.2211.03148_1c89425b1e0b420247ff1d4566b7d: In recent years, there has been rapid advancement in the field of Deep Learning; subsequently, enormous headway has been made in applying computer vision techniques to medical imaging
elements.2211.03148_254527092ea0e82b9c3d4ce03bc4d: Different algorithms have been developed and fine-tuned for various diseases
elements.2211.03148_73bcdd4279a37c7ec929c1453e7bd: A critical problem in biomedical image analysis is the occurrence of batch effects
elements.2211.03148_b38c2f79a3e44f56ad9e22d8649b1: , which are differences introduced through technological artifacts among different subsets of data
elements.2211.03148_2cc443a8c94227a451f674d8721bc: Sample handling and data collecting techniques make applying computer vision algorithms to data from different pathological labs problematic, which is an essential step in developing ML models
elements.2211.03148_99390aae063310adbe88c5b4a32d8: Diabetic Retinopathy (DR) is a common disease that causes vision loss or, in some cases, even blindness among people with diabetes, affecting 415 million people
elements.2211.03148_ac02f23c1cc0949e99c2075c00cb3: Automated detection of DR is essential to limit the progression of DR by conducting early diagnoses on diabetic patients, as the normal procedure by ophthalmologists demands many resources
elements.2211.03148_c89b3fe8a21cad83842c556952300: Therefore, the interest in employing deep neural networks to automatically classify Diabetic Retinopathy has grown over the past few years
elements.2211.03148_f2fb2de5ff8ead4091ea822bf903a: A well-calibrated classifier would place less probability mass on uncertain classes
elements.2211.03148_3fa7df47405ce6db46be241f572af: The issue of uncertainty estimation is especially important in the medical domain in order to trust confident model predictions for screening automation and referring uncertain cases for manual intervention of a medical expert
elements.2211.03148_6fc9ccaa6995795a07a7839e3892c: Bayesian probability theory offers a sound mathematical framework to design machine learning models with an inherent and explicit notion of uncertainty
elements.2211.03148_213621797fc590312ee39b7ec2477: Instead of resulting in a single per-class probability, such models can estimate the moments of the output distribution for every class, including mean and variance
elements.2211.03148_b7eed683e014529643b8d67e6e45d: Multiple probabilistic and Bayesian methods such as
elements.2211.03148_b9d114040da091b4aed0a011a7ae3: have been proposed to quantify the uncertainty estimates
elements.2211.03148_8788b359a42e92d44a3cb6927c982: The ensemble of networks can further improve the performance of models
elements.2211.03148_fb74bd3fd01a0e2a08fd5e7598560: There has been some work on incorporating uncertainty where ensemble methods
elements.2211.03148_33289834b027247591e4701da28da: learned multiple tasks by using the uncertainty predicted as weights for the losses of each of the models, thus outperforming individual models trained on each task
elements.2211.03148_b41f7d1555d835ca307dd0897a661: Non-Bayesian alternatives can offer simpler yet effective means to quantify the uncertainties of DNNs
elements.2211.03148_81186b8cc1f2ebdff22edd19a3525: While the ensemble approach is simple and easy to implement, it is typically costly to work with many networks during training and inference
elements.2211.03148_bd3530337f291cda4006155f8eb5a: Here, we introduce a reliable end-to-end framework for the classification of Diabetic Retinopathy fundus images that combines the concepts of TTAug
elements.2211.03148_123c0a5efceb70db647943919af65: , allowing us to obtain a reliable, well-calibrated final prediction by making the final ensemble of predictions aware of the model's inherent uncertainty
elements.2211.03148_04502dc764e2527f0361417ac465d: The novelty of our approach lies in it's ability to produce well-calibrated reliable results without compromising on model's efficacy.

elements.2211.03148_178d775ed7045fc3b8373e6b78772: We believe there is potential for this model architecture to be incorporated using Bayesian methods for various tasks involving classification and regression
elements.2211.03148_9e4f4b60db1c2c4b90e6ede21cf8f: We hope our work helps the community and inspires further research on uncertainty-aware learning of the model as well as making more reliable models for medical diagnosis.
elements.2211.03148_7a1105b400f6ed845394e10ea0427: The approach introduced in this paper aims at tackling the issue of over-confident predictions during model outcomes for the diagnosis of Diabetic Retinopathy
elements.2211.03148_4886bd566df043171dbeb178413b0: Identifying Diabetic Retinopathy is one healthcare application where machine learning has already shown significant potential
elements.2211.03148_f744e2b4e2f1fa2766c8ca2d0b2ae: However, its applications in high-stakes healthcare choices must incorporate systematic uncertainty quantification and calibration for robust evaluation
elements.2211.03148_6116add429299f5db56ea6a8079c7: By calibrating more generalized models, this framework also significantly aids in risk appraisal, lowering the possibility of potential misdiagnosis
elements.2211.03148_1a839e50dbd7373c142dcce8f4e0b: We hope our work advances the current onset procedure for detecting Diabetic Retinopathy while also bringing trustworthy interpretations to other medical imaging procedures.

elements.2211.03148_2b4907f69223daa3c731a83d38bd1: Did you describe any potential participant risks, with links to Institutional Review Board (IRB) approvals, if applicable?
elements.2211.03148_6a5ac3efb7c3cdd888c79cc24d16f: Did you include the estimated hourly wage paid to participants and the total amount spent on participant compensation?
elements.2211.03148_6abcc105a10dc7ffacbb9e7177d1d: Optionally include extra information (complete proofs, additional experiments and plots) in the appendix
elements.2211.03148_dabda49d6e41cbfdd5da6ea5c74ec: This section will often be part of the supplemental material.
